# AI in the Real World

#### After learning about analyzing data, students explore how AI models process data and the role of specialized hardware in optimizing performance. They analyze an AI model, learn about different processing units, and test their capabilities in various tasks. 

## Real-world Scenarios 

#### AI systems use data to make decisions in real-world applications. 
#### Let’s explore how different AI models function and what data they rely on.

