## AI and Data 

#### Choose one of the scenarios above and consider:

>- #### What is the AI model doing in this scenario?
>- #### What type of data is being input?
>- #### What does this AI system do with the data?
>- #### Why does this task require speed and scale?


## AI and Hardware

#### After examining these real-world scenarios, students should recognize the importance of optimizing AI systems. Next, they’ll explore which types of hardware are best suited for powering and improving AI performance.


